column.Name: StyleCostingScenarioItemID
column.lookupquery: SELECT ScenarioID, StyleCostingName FROM vwx_StyleCosting_SEL WHERE StyleCostingTypeID = 5 AND StyleID = ##ID##

column.Name: StyleSKUItemID
